test_zero_range:
assert [0] == []
  Left contains one more item: 0
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [0]
  ?  +
test_large_range:
assert [1] == [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
  Right contains 4 more items, first extra item: 2
  Full diff:
  - [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
  + [1]
test_even_range:
assert [2] == [2, 4, 6, 8, 10]
  Right contains 4 more items, first extra item: 4
  Full diff:
  - [2, 4, 6, 8, 10]
  + [2]
